      "properties": {
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "STICKER SHEET FROM MULTIPLE LOGOS\n\nPacks three separate transparent assets into one print-ready sticker\nsheet, plus a checkerboard preview so you can see it before saving.\n\nFlow: three Load Image -> Mask Adapter -> Trim chains -> batch the\nimages together and the masks together -> Sticker Sheet Builder ->\nMask Adapter -> Join Image With Alpha -> Save Image.\n\nSet before running:\n  - The three Load Image nodes: swap in your own assets\n  - Sticker Sheet Builder: layout (\"grid\" or \"packed\"), sheet_width/\n    height, margin, padding\n\nTo add a fourth asset: copy one Load Image -> Mask Adapter -> Trim\nchain, then chain one more Image Batch / Mask Batch pair in before\nSticker Sheet Builder, the same way the second and third assets are\nmerged in below."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653",
      "title": "README"
    },
